Available Tools: get_lab_results | get_latest_results | get_result_history | download_report
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "patient_id": "string", "test_type": "string", "from_date": "string" }
Response Schema: { "results": [{ "test": "string", "value": number, "unit": "string", "reference_range": "string", "status": "normal|high|low" }] }
---
Question: Obtain the most recent uric acid measurement for patient P-2045.
Call: { "func_call": "get_latest_results", "patient_id": "P-2045", "test_type": "uric_acid", "from_date": "" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "Uric Acid", "value": 7.8, "unit": "mg/dL", "reference_range": "3.5-7.2", "status": "high" }] }

Question: Review the historical ferritin levels for patient P-8812 starting from February 15th, 2023 to assess iron stores.
Call: { "func_call": "get_result_history", "patient_id": "P-8812", "test_type": "ferritin", "from_date": "2023-02-15" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "Ferritin", "value": 15, "unit": "ng/mL", "reference_range": "30-300", "status": "low" }, { "test": "Ferritin", "value": 22, "unit": "ng/mL", "reference_range": "30-300", "status": "low" }, { "test": "Ferritin", "value": 45, "unit": "ng/mL", "reference_range": "30-300", "status": "normal" }] }

